[[Baha'u'llah]] me simba nde mono kele [[ngunza]] ya nsuka na ndonga ya bangunza ([[Zaratustra]], [[Krisna]], [[Mose]], [[Buda]], [[Yesu]] ye [[Muhammad]]).

